Package: MRMOSS
Type: Package
Title: Scalable Joint Mendelian Randomization of Correlated Outcomes Using Summary Statistics
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-06-04
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yunlong", "Cao", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "157203291+YunlongCao@users.noreply.github.com")
    )
Author: Yunlong Cao
Maintainer: Yunlong Cao <157203291+YunlongCao@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: MR-MOSS fits a likelihood-based multi-outcome Mendelian
    randomization model using harmonized GWAS summary statistics. It jointly
    models SNP-exposure and SNP-outcome association estimates with a working
    outcome correlation matrix, and provides outcome-specific, subset/domain-level
    and all-outcome likelihood-ratio tests for correlated outcome panels.
